<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="frank-adj">frank <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /fræŋk/    美 /fræŋk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>坦白的；直率的</strong></h4>
<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="to-be-frank">to be frank</h3>
<p>1.<strong>坦白说；坦率地说：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>To be frank,everyone suffers from stress at some time in their life.
坦率地说，每个人在生活中某个时候都会有压力。</p><footer>北师大新必修① – 1</footer></div></div>